<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Your Trust Healthcare API Key</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #212529;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #007bff;
      }
      .api-key {
        font-size: 16px;
        background-color: #f1f3f5;
        border: 1px dashed #007bff;
        padding: 12px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        word-break: break-all;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #000;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6c757d;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Welcome to Trust Healthcare Developer Platform</h2>

      <p>Hi <%= ownerName %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for registering your application with Trust Healthcare.</p>

      <p>Your unique API key is:</p>

      <div class="api-key"><%= apiKey %></div>

      <p>
        Please store this key securely. Youâ€™ll need it to authenticate your
        requests to our API.
      </p>

      <p>
        For security reasons, do not share this key publicly. If you believe
        your key has been compromised, request a new one immediately.
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        Need help? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:support@trusthealthcare.com"
          >support@trusthealthcare.com</a
        ><br />
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Trust Healthcare. All rights
        reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
